    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single gap (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is acknowledged and documented. The assessment team determined that the single-condition limitation does not invalidate the overall credibility conclusion given the direct correspondence between the validation configuration and the ASTM F1717 regulatory benchmark. The model is accepted for use in support of pre-market submission activities.",
